OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTruss' top aide won't be   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpaid via lobbying firm     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The prime minister's chief of staff    
OL,6, will now be employed directly by the   
OL,7, government instead of through a private
OL,8, company, Downing Street has confirmed. 
OL,10,FIt follows the revelation that Mark    
OL,11,FFullbrook was being paid through his   
OL,12,Flobbying firm, Fullbrook Strategies.   
OL,14,FThe arrangement had been criticised by 
OL,15,Fthe opposition and by some within the  
OL,16,FConservative party.                    
OL,18,FNo 10 has said Mr Fullbrook will be put
OL,19,Fon a special advisor contract to avoid 
OL,20,F"any ongoing speculation".             
